Package: sffdr
Type: Package
Title: Surrogate Functional False Discovery Rates for Genome-Wide Studies
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(person("Andrew", "Bass", email ="ab3105@cam.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre")),
             person("Chris", "Wallace", email ="chris.wallace@cam.ac.uk", role = c("aut")))
Maintainer: Andrew Bass <ab3105@cam.ac.uk>
Description: Leveraging informative variables to improve power in genome-wide studies using the surrogate functional false discovery rate (sfFDR) framework. sfFDR builds from the fFDR methodology to estimate FDR quantities given many informative variables. Our non-parametric approach can handle a large number of p-values and multiple informative variables.
URL: https://github.com/ajbass/sffdr
License: LGPL
Encoding: UTF-8
